
 Function Reference


 Array functions.

	array explode ( string $delimiter, string $string [, int $limit = PHP_INT_MAX] )

		Returns an array of strings, each of which is a substring of string formed by splitting it on boundaries formed by
		the string delimiter. 


 	string implode(string $glue, array $elements);
	string implode(array $elements);

		Join array elements with the glue string.


 	
